rted the transform, then added more documents afterward, possibly while also changing the transform's capacity or node configuration. The transform is running searches regularly, but the checkpoint isn't advancing to process those 2 pending documents. For a continuous sync transform with a 1-second delay, checkpoint 2 should trigger once those documents are ready. I should check the source index directly to see what's actually there and understand why the checkpoint progression is stalled.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3697,"cache_read_input_tokens":41743,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3697},"output_tokens":23,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"76f3b3ad-df3a-4830-a932-a070652945d9","uuid":"ca6a8173-9de0-4d14-af0f-a8889b009c49","request_id":"req_011CcQfeaYceWBFRfX9mhw2M"}
